Heat oven to 350 degrees F (175 degrees C). Combine chicken, artichokes, 1 cup mozzarella, Parmesan and tomatoes in large bowl. Mix Cooking Creme, garlic powder and 2 tablespoons basil in medium bowl until blended. Gradually whisk in milk. Stir half into chicken mixture. Pour half the remaining Cooking Creme mixture into 13x9-inch baking dish; cover with 3 noodles and 1/3 of the chicken mixture. Repeat layers of noodles and chicken mixture twice; top with remaining noodles, Cooking Creme mixture and mozzarella. Cover. Bake 25 minutes or until heated through, uncovering for the last 5 minutes. Sprinkle with basil; let stand 5 minutes before serving.